      <section eId="sec_13_2_1">
        <num>13-2-1</num>
        <content>
          <p>The construction of a contract is a question of law for the court. Where any matter of fact is involved, the jury should find the fact.</p>
          <p>(Orig. Code 1863, § 2718; Code 1868, § 2712; Code 1873, § 2754; Code 1882, § 2754; Civil Code 1895, § 3672; Civil Code 1910, § 4265; Code 1933, § 20-701.)</p>
